### **3. 27_LogRhythmAnalyzer**  
**Description:**  
Parses logs and identifies repeated messages or bursts of similar entries over time.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LogRhythmAnalyzer - Log Frequency & Pattern Detection

LogRhythmAnalyzer reads logs and shows frequency breakdowns to help find persistent or abnormal behavior.

## Features
- Group by message repetition  
- Keyword alerts  
- Lightweight CLI parser  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/27_LogRhythmAnalyzer.git
cd 27_LogRhythmAnalyzer
python analyze.py logs/system.log
